{"tid":432214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「男神」黃子揚幫林俊賢養仔14年　好友反目變襟兄弟","createTime":"2017-10-11T10:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T12:05:22.000Z","uid":129072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d0805e6b04e93ac506ba53ad5fb805b49a494d","tid":432214,"uid":129072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171010/large/1507649219_f438.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171010%2Flarge%2F1507649219_f438.jpg&h=042bbe47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在電影中經常做反派，被封娛圈十大惡人的黃子揚九月被爆再婚，與比他細二十年大陸經理人入紙註冊，但原來這個新老婆並非第二春，係第三春至真！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/181720_0f08e0f3b7da125b7e2226209a460480.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F181720_0f08e0f3b7da125b7e2226209a460480.png&h=23b238a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據知，年過半百的黃子揚，其實一直收埋了十多年的第二任老婆Winnie，想當年惠英紅都是她手下敗將，而這個Winnie亦嫁過俾八十年代靚仔小生林俊賢，更在二○○○年生咗個仔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/181800_685b812f91dd8de3697497f09955313c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F181800_685b812f91dd8de3697497f09955313c.jpg&h=7b5e5886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃子揚同林俊賢這對襟兄弟從此反目，之後黃子揚更接收了Winnie與她的囝囝，甘願做林俊賢兒子後父多年，視如己出，而這個秘密埋藏多年，終於被爆出！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20171011/553620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20171011%2F553620&d=CLfogiUcjJF%2FuRmxAIjHDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=43f1cca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20171011%2F553620&h=13eeea9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20171011/553620</a>"},{"pid":"d21a4a27f9b49cdbb722b4419c2b6308a2805a46","tid":432214,"uid":129072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"林俊賢女友認同黃子揚結過婚 大讚對方是稱職後父<br />\n　<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171011/large/1507706786_b0e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F1507706786_b0e8.jpg&h=2820d4a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩年前，林俊賢接受《壹》仔訪問，提到自己輸掉身家連親情都輸掉，又講到有女朋友與他生下一名兒子後，遇上自己輸掉股票致破產，最終這位女朋友帶着兒子離開，而這個女人就是黃子揚第二任妻子Winnie。<br />\n<br />\n記：林俊賢當年同你生咗個仔，你哋嗰時有冇結婚？<br />\n<br />\nWinnie：我都覺得唔係好方便交代，或者你問番林俊賢。<br />\n<br />\n記：子揚一直做緊後父？<br />\n<br />\nWinnie：都係，佢係好盡爸爸嘅責任，呢方面可以俾番一個讚佢。<br />\n<br />\n記：你同子揚之後有結婚？<br />\n<br />\nWinnie：都係！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20171011/553785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20171011%2F553785&d=CLfogiUcjJF%2FuRmxAIjHDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a40561e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20171011%2F553785&h=58c22b8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20171011/553785</a>"},{"pid":"8b02b4290fedb65d77cb186781b203de60f6232e","tid":432214,"uid":154456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6090795994643396b6141cbd96916a3918054bfc","tid":432214,"uid":138729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"點妻Tina 係咪 How many what did you 扑him last night個條鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好熟口面"},{"pid":"ca361dd194789418dd3d48d68dd6f57655863768","tid":432214,"uid":39431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點妻Tina 係咪 How many what did you 扑him last night個條鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好熟口面</blockquote><br />\n完全係  但google過搵唔到其他資料